name: Broken LCD at the Train Station
description: I was walking in the tunnel under the train station of my city when I spotted this broken LCD. My reaction's been like: "Man, that's some dope NFT hanging right there! It's so beautifully broken!". I took some photos of it, chosen the best one, did some work on the colors, added a few WMs and BOOM! There it is. Then, as I fineshed I started asking my self: "Who in the he*k knows what happened in that tunnel to make those beautiful cracks!?"; "Did someone lost his train and furiously punched that screen!?"; "Did some guys brawl after some alcohol excess!?" No one knows, but those cracks sure have some story behind.
